column13:
Properkeys Limited, is a property sourcing company. We source off-market properties for our clients (“buyers”). When someone contacts Properkeys, they may want to know how they may go about getting registered with our company, or possibly what properties we may have in stock. Maybe, a landlord contacts us wanting to list his property on our website. Our process goes as follows:
1.	Upon initial engagement with our prospect, we schedule (either by phone or via the website) a 15min call. The purpose of this call is to discuss what requirements they have when searching for a property.
2.	We capture our prospect’s requirements in our CRM database. Once the call is ended, we send them an Email summarising their requirements with a copy of our contract.
3.	The client must return a signed copy of this contract to info@properkeys.co.uk in order for Properkeys to begin their search
a.	By signing the contract, our now client gives permission for Properkeys to carry out a bespoke search on their behalf. By signing the contract, Properkeys is saying we are committed to putting in the time and effort into finding them the right property
4.	If they express the need for an accountant, broker or solicitor, we will send them a separate Email referring them to one of our partners
5.	Once the signed contract is received, we begin their bespoke property search. We are bargain hunters, so we will always search for the best possible deals. More importantly, deals that meet all their requirements!
6.	We aim to find our client a property in the quickest time possible. After we have sourced the property, we stack the deal and present to them the numbers. If they are happy with the offer, they will pay 20% of the finder’s fee to hold the property. Once they’ve viewed the property, if they are satisfied, they will pay the remainder of that finder’s fee, ultimately closing the deal.

6.	We aim to find our client a property in the quickest time possible. After we have sourced the property, we stack the deal and present to them the numbers. If they are happy with the offer, they will pay 20% of the finder’s fee to hold the property. Once they’ve viewed the property, if they are satisfied, they will pay the remainder of that finder’s fee, ultimately closing the deal.


Email address: info@properkeys.co.uk

Kemp LLP is a newly formed boutique international law firm established by former partners of Stephenson Harwood LLP and Winston & Strawn LLP, which operates out of two leading centres of international business and finance – Hong Kong and London. The firm covers a wide variety of practice areas that span from transactions to disputes. Within the area of disputes, M.B. Kemp has the capability to cover both non-contentious and contentious matters, including domestic and international litigation, mediation and arbitration. 

Contentious Practice Areas
 
•	International Arbitration

ONO - pronounced Oh No! Is an app based product that helps those involved in a road traffic accident collect the correct data at the roadside. 
We help the user stay clam and lead them through all the relevant questions needed gently and intuitively. This information then feeds through to fleet owners/insurers/brokers who need to manage this data. 
Our software will alert fleet managers to an incident and will help them process this data, removing the need for paper processes and a messy chain of action. 
We charge fleet owners

Activity:      Reform Pursuit, are a non-profit organisation with the fundamental intention of pushing for reforms to current UK laws to improve and combat institutionalised racism. As a collective, we have decided to take the initiative and do something tangible and practical about it. 
We are a small diverse team of individuals from different backgrounds that share one common goal, a pragmatic approach to tackling racism via lawful means. We came together and concluded that the fundamental concept of Reform Pursuit would result in one positive step forward for race relations with measurable, tangible results. Societies' behaviour is governed by the laws of the land, therefore a key step to address racism is via lawful reforms, where applicable, raising public awareness and empowering impacted communities.
Reform Pursuit is committed to the following;

Greeting:  Welcome to Insemigen Ltd, how can I help you today?  


Response: I am afraid there is no one available to take your call at the moment, can I take your details and get someone to call you back shortly? 

Response: Thankyou. I will arrange for someone to call you back as soon as possible. In the meantime, you could also send an Email to info@insemigen.com 

  
Business Activity: 
Research, development and innovation in animal genetics and breeding services 

Insemigen Ltd are market-leading innovators in animal genetics and animal breeding services. We are driven by science, but led by compassion, to improve animal lives and achieve new excellence in breeding. Our core mission is to improve the genetics and breeding practices of domestic animal species, for the betterment of animal health, welfare and production. Animal health and welfare is at the core of everything that we do, and we are passionate about improving animal breeding practices, for both animal and human health, and for future generations of both animals and people. 

 
Names: No particular Names to note. 

Email: 	info@insemigen.com

Activity:    PDF Estates Ltd was established in December 2015, by Peter Beisty and Darren Fields, to meet with the specific needs and requirements of both landlords and tenants in the UK. They pride themselves on providing a transparent service, with no hidden fees or charges, whilst ensuring that all properties feel like a proper home for their tenants. Testament to their success is their portfolio of happy and long-term landlords and tenants. Their longest serving tenant has been with them for over 20 years and continues to enjoy the services and the property that they offer.

column13:
Growth Mindset is an e-learning platform designed to offer live online classes of soft skills for kids aged between 8 to 15. Growth Mindset's platform connects learners and parents to certified independent instructors leading live classes in small groups. Through Growth Mindset, families can choose their instructors and classes for group learning based on their needs and interests at a lower price point than private tutoring.

We offer our products in Education Institutions & HR departments of Medium-large business.

With Growth Mindset for Employers, employees can focus on their work, knowing their kids are engaged and enhancing their soft skills through interactive classes taught live via video by Growth Mindset instructors.

Growth Mindset for educational institutions can offer unique elective classes or just-right small-group tutoring sessions without finding the budget to hire hundreds of additional instructors trained in soft skills.

Business Activity:  For prospective clients asking for the services we provide, please take a note of the following:   We are a regulated business with licenses issued in the UK and Hong Kong for providing business services, including offshore and onshore company formation, business and private  bank account opening. On top of these, we also provide any auxiliary services, such as online business matching ,online business consulting, education services, trademark registration. Our clientele is mainly high-net-wealth individuals, their family, and the companies they run.

Thank you for calling Taylor Property Holdings Group Ltd, how can I help you? 

If they are calling off the back of a letter they have received:

If they ask “where did you get my details”:

We use the Land Registry to find the details of the land owner we want to contact.

Response: Can you please give me the reference number at the bottom of the letter you have received so we can locate you in our system?

Great, thank you.
I will see if there is someone available to deal with your enquiry.

***please call my mobile 07817669795***

Response if I am not available:

I am afraid there is no one available to take your call at the moment, can I take your details and get someone to call you back shortly?

***END CALL***

If it is a call for any other reason:

Greeting:  Thank you for calling Taylor Property Holdings Group Ltd, how can I help you? 

Response: Ok thank you, let me see if there is someone who can assist you with your enquiry.

***please call my mobile 07817669795***

Response if I am not available:

***END CALL***
